            "description": "Foydalanuvchi rollarini yangilash.\nRuxsat etilgan rollar: ROLE_USER, ROLE_BUSINESS_OWNER, ROLE_ADMIN\nBu so'rov audit logga USER_ROLE_CHANGED sifatida yoziladi."
